summary: An ordinance relating to and amending Plat 219E page 4 of the Official Zoning Map of the City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property in Lots 9-13 incl., Block 17, Lots 9-13 incl., Block 18, all in North Seattle Heights, Unrec., located on the south side of No. 137th St. from Interlake Ave. to Midvale Ave., from Duplex Residence High Density (RD 5000) Zone to General Commercial (CG) Zone.
